      <p class="gbc-disc"><strong>Methodology &amp; data.</strong> Figures reflect closed transactions in the MLS for the Gulf &amp; Bay Club Bayside subdivision, sourced from Stellar MLS via the Adamson Group data pipeline. "CDOM" is cumulative days on market; "SP/LP" is sale price to list price. The headline snapshot uses a 180-day window; the transaction ledger and quarterly trend use trailing 12 months, computed as of July 14, 2026. "Minimum Lease Period" is the value most frequently reported on MLS listings in this association and is <em>not</em> a substitute for the condo documents — confirm current rental rules with the association before purchasing. Small communities close few units per quarter, so single sales can move averages meaningfully. Data is provided for informational purposes and is not a guarantee of value.</p>
